    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it is in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014it basically still has that new-car smell! It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. I'm looking for a quick sale to a good home, so I've priced it to move. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin\u2014I promise you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43800.0,
