    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo represents a rare opportunity to own a preserved icon of Japanese engineering. Under the hood lies the legendary 2JZ-GTE, a 3.0L longitudinal inline-six featuring sequential twin-turbochargers and an air-to-air intercooler, delivering linear power through the sought-after Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains taut, riding on factory-calibrated double-wishbone suspension at all four corners, while the rear-mounted Torsen limited-slip differential ensures optimal torque distribution. Every component, from the four-piston front calipers to the untouched wire looms, reflects a level of maintenance consistent with its showroom-quality status. This is a mechanically pristine example with zero modifications, retaining its original forced-induction mapping and cooling efficiency.",
      "price": 43500.0,
